00:21:48.700 --> 00:21:50.116
And that is one
hell of a designer

00:21:50.116 --> 00:21:51.158
who's got a track record.

00:21:51.158 --> 00:21:52.990
DORON KAGAN: Even feature
will not help now.

00:21:52.990 --> 00:21:53.870
ANDY PAYNE: No, no.

00:21:53.870 --> 00:21:54.510
CHRIS SOUTHALL:
That's a good point,

00:21:54.510 --> 00:21:55.930
because what you were
talking about earlier.

