00:23:15.480 --> 00:23:19.427
We see games that are paymium,
where you buy the game

00:23:19.427 --> 00:23:21.010
and then you can buy
in-app purchases.

00:23:21.010 --> 00:23:23.176
We see games that are
supported by in-app purchases.

00:23:23.176 --> 00:23:25.260
And we see games that
are actually premium.

00:23:25.260 --> 00:23:28.360
What business
models are missing?

00:23:28.360 --> 00:23:31.735
Is there something else that
we should be thinking about?

00:23:31.735 --> 00:23:32.860
SAAD CHOUDRI: Subscription.

00:23:32.860 --> 00:23:34.390
DAN GALPIN: And subscription,
of course, is actually--

00:23:34.390 --> 00:23:35.806
DORON KAGAN: It's
