00:23:37.030 --> 00:23:39.140
SAAD CHOUDRI: Why not? "World
of Warcraft" did it for a while.

00:23:39.140 --> 00:23:40.431
DORON KAGAN: Yeah, for a while.

00:23:40.431 --> 00:23:41.790
But the world is changing.

00:23:41.790 --> 00:23:42.600
SAAD CHOUDRI: The
world is changing.

00:23:42.600 --> 00:23:44.433
CHRIS SOUTHALL: I think
if you skew younger,

00:23:44.433 --> 00:23:46.520
