they choose the list of games

00:24:19.950 --> 00:24:22.000
that they think are good games.

00:24:22.000 --> 00:24:23.240
It's free subscription.

00:24:23.240 --> 00:24:26.280
So why would anybody pay
for any game service that

00:24:26.280 --> 00:24:29.920
would limit him to 100
games or 1,000 games?

00:24:29.920 --> 00:24:32.055
SAAD CHOUDRI: I was talking
