type platform.

00:24:33.604 --> 00:24:34.520
DORON KAGAN: One game.

00:24:34.520 --> 00:24:36.260
SAAD CHOUDRI: Yeah.

00:24:36.260 --> 00:24:39.350
ANDY PAYNE: So one of
the questions I had is,

00:24:39.350 --> 00:24:41.440
