very conscious of it.

00:25:15.510 --> 00:25:17.480
We've been COPPA
compliant since we started

00:25:17.480 --> 00:25:21.210
and it's crucial for
us to maintain that.

00:25:21.210 --> 00:25:26.010
And also, it's a hard
audience to the service

00:25:26.010 --> 00:25:28.177
now because there's so many
apps out there for free.

00:25:28.177 --> 00:25:29.593
CHRIS SOUTHALL:
And that's why you

00:25:29.593 --> 00:25:32.050
start talking about subscription
and you go back to paid.

00:25:32.050 --> 00:25:35.280
Especially if you go much
younger than sort of 15,

00:25:35.280 --> 00:25:36.170
in reality.

00:25:36.170 --> 00:25:38.785
Is it's an open
question, I think.

00:25:38.785 --> 00:25:40.160
ANDY PAYNE: It
feels like there's

00:25:40.160 --> 00:25:44.040
a paid app market
